The dean makes an appearance to thank recruiters for their support of the university, contributing to this lively setting. Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the event, including the dean's interaction with the recruiters. Nearby, some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, while consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables. Students also compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers.

Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the event, including the dean's engagement with the recruiters, who remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Nearby, some students quietly rehearse elevator pitches against the wall, while alumni volunteers provide quick pep talks near the coffee station. Consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables, enhancing the lively setting. Additionally, students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers, and workshops on networking etiquette occur in an adjoining classroom, further adding to the dynamic energy of the event.

Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the event, including the dean's interactions with the recruiters, who remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Nearby, some students quietly rehearse elevator pitches against the wall, while alumni volunteers provide quick pep talks near a coffee station. Consulting firms display glossy case study booklets on high tables, contributing to the lively setting. Workshops on networking etiquette occur in an adjoining classroom, further adding to the dynamic energy. Small groups of students analyze which recruiters appeared most enthusiastic, enhancing the overall engagement of the event.
